<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Melita International.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Melita International.</headline>
<dateline>LOS ANGELES 1997-07-10</dateline>
<text>
<p>Robertson Stephens &amp; Co research analyst John Powers has started coverage of Melita International Corp with a buy rating.</p>
<p>-- In a statement, Powers said the provider of computer systems for telemarketing and other communications is growing along with the telemarketing industry and expanding into other computer telephony products.</p>
<p>-- said its products improve customer service, boost efficiency and cuts costs. Estimates 1997 earnings at $0.47 a share and 1998 earnings at $0.58 a share.</p>
<p>-- Melita shares were up 1/4 at 12-1/4.</p>
</text>
